{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "7a1c2d3e-4f5a-6b7c-8d9e-0f1a2b3c4d5e",
    "name": "Tempus API",
    "description": "Colección completa de la API Tempus (e-commerce de relojería, UADE).\n\n## Variables de la colección\n- `baseUrl`: http://localhost:4002\n- `authToken`: se captura automáticamente al ejecutar Login\n- `cartId`, `productId`, `orderId`, `discountId`: IDs reusables\n\n## Cómo usar\n1. Arrancá la app (`./mvnw spring-boot:run`) y MySQL (`docker start tempus-mysql`).\n2. Ejecutá **Auth > Login Buyer** o **Login Admin**. El script post-response guarda el token en `{{authToken}}`.\n3. Los endpoints protegidos usan `Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}` automáticamente.\n4. Para probar 401/403, corré un endpoint protegido tras limpiar la variable (botón de eye→edit).\n\n## Usuarios seed\n- admin / admin123 (ROLE_ADMIN)\n- buyer1 / buyer123 (ROLE_BUYER)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:4002", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "authToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "productId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "cartId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "orderId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "discountId", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "2", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [ { "key": "token", "value": "{{authToken}}", "type": "string" } ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Registro, login y logout. Los endpoints son públicos salvo logout.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (new user)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"newuser{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"email\": \"newuser{{$timestamp}}@tempus.local\",\n  \"password\": \"test1234\",\n  \"name\": \"Nuevo\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Usuario\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","register"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201 creado', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200, 201]);",
                  "});",
                  "if (pm.response.code < 400) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body && body.token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('authToken', body.token);",
                  "        console.log('authToken guardado tras register');",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Admin",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('devuelve token', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('token');",
                  "});",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('authToken', body.token);",
                  "    console.log('authToken (admin) guardado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Buyer",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"buyer1\",\n  \"password\": \"buyer123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('authToken', body.token);",
                  "    console.log('authToken (buyer) guardado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (credenciales inválidas) — espera 401",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"buyer1\",\n  \"password\": \"WRONG\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('401 UNAUTHORIZED', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(401); });",
                  "pm.test('código CREDENCIALES_INVALIDAS', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().codigo).to.eql('CREDENCIALES_INVALIDAS');",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","logout"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
